Resource Profile: Fee for Value Initative

Official URL: http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/ffv-initative-resource Version: 7.0.0
Active as of 2022-09-06 Computable Name: FFVInitiative

Health Data Connect Common Data Model definition of what fields we currently define for an FFV initiative record

Usage:

  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Contract/ExampleFFVInitiative, Contract/Milestone1Initiative

Description of Profiles, Differentials, Snapshots and how the different presentations work.
